394
00:19:26,299 --> 00:19:29,039
[SPEAKER_01] Danas nam Evropa

395
00:19:29,039 --> 00:19:30,420
[SPEAKER_01] kroji pravdu

396
00:19:30,420 --> 00:19:31,599
