399
00:19:36,339 --> 00:19:38,240
[SPEAKER_01] nego mnogi evropski narodi.

400
00:19:38,240 --> 00:19:40,140
[SPEAKER_01] Prije Rusa,

401
00:19:40,140 --> 00:19:41,480
[SPEAKER_01] prije Poljaka,

402
