672
00:26:29,660 --> 00:26:30,900
[SPEAKER_01] Torinsko platno.

673
00:26:30,900 --> 00:26:31,660
[SPEAKER_01] Znači,

674
00:26:31,660 --> 00:26:32,640
[SPEAKER_01] u grobu nemaš ništa.

675
00:26:35,599 --> 00:26:36,460
[SPEAKER_01] kako je vjera pala

676
