[SPEAKER_01] u to vrijeme?

677
00:26:37,039 --> 00:26:40,779
[SPEAKER_01] Papa pokreće vojnu

678
00:26:40,779 --> 00:26:42,079
[SPEAKER_01] da se osobađa

679
00:26:42,079 --> 00:26:42,839
[SPEAKER_01] Isusov grob.

680
00:26:42,839 --> 00:26:43,640
[SPEAKER_01] A zbog čega?

681
00:26:45,579 --> 00:26:46,839
[SPEAKER_01] U grobu nema nikoga.

682
00:26:46,839 --> 00:26:48,880
[SPEAKER_01] Dugestva je da Isus

683
