[SPEAKER_01] ostao u grobu.

684
00:26:49,619 --> 00:26:50,619
[SPEAKER_01] Mi vremo da Isus

685
00:26:50,619 --> 00:26:51,920
[SPEAKER_01] uskrsnuo dušom,

686
00:26:51,920 --> 00:26:53,160
[SPEAKER_01] tijelom, kostijima,

687
00:26:53,160 --> 00:26:54,000
[SPEAKER_01] kako ćeš mesom

688
00:26:54,000 --> 00:26:54,579
[SPEAKER_01] da to nazvati.

689
00:26:54,579 --> 00:26:56,039
[SPEAKER_01] Nema ništa u grobu.

690
00:26:56,039 --> 00:26:58,140
[SPEAKER_01] Opet Bog kaže

691
00:26:58,140 --> 00:26:58,539
