705
00:27:20,539 --> 00:27:21,480
[SPEAKER_01] bogatu crkvu.

706
00:27:21,480 --> 00:27:23,299
[SPEAKER_01] Radi se o vremenu

707
00:27:23,299 --> 00:27:24,720
[SPEAKER_01] Pape Inocenta Treček,

708
00:27:24,720 --> 00:27:27,039
[SPEAKER_01] koji je

709
00:27:27,039 --> 00:27:28,160
