713
00:27:32,859 --> 00:27:33,640
[SPEAKER_01] kompletno rukama.

714
00:27:33,640 --> 00:27:34,339
[SPEAKER_01] Bez njega se ništa

715
00:27:34,339 --> 00:27:35,460
[SPEAKER_01] u Evropi ne može događati.

716
00:27:35,460 --> 00:27:37,920
[SPEAKER_01] Silno bogatstvo crkve.

717
00:27:37,920 --> 00:27:40,039
[SPEAKER_01] U to vreme

718
00:27:40,039 --> 00:27:40,900
[SPEAKER_01] Bog podiže jednoga

719
00:27:40,900 --> 00:27:42,180
[SPEAKER_01] siromašnog čovjeka,

720
00:27:42,180 --> 00:27:43,500
