[SPEAKER_01] ali drugačijom metodom.

735
00:28:09,779 --> 00:28:10,720
[SPEAKER_01] Metoda je bitna.

736
00:28:10,720 --> 00:28:12,359
[SPEAKER_01] Metodom ljubavi.

737
00:28:12,359 --> 00:28:15,039
[SPEAKER_01] On dolazi sultanu.

738
00:28:15,039 --> 00:28:16,559
[SPEAKER_01] Metoda sile,

739
00:28:16,920 --> 00:28:18,039
[SPEAKER_01] koju papa primjenjuje,

740
00:28:18,039 --> 00:28:19,779
