[SPEAKER_01] I sve što ste čuli

742
00:28:21,460 --> 00:28:22,740
[SPEAKER_01] o križarskim ratovima,

743
00:28:22,740 --> 00:28:24,400
[SPEAKER_01] to je pravo čudo.

744
00:28:24,400 --> 00:28:26,599
[SPEAKER_01] Kako je to uopće crka

745
00:28:26,599 --> 00:28:27,039
[SPEAKER_01] obstala?

746
00:28:27,039 --> 00:28:28,460
[SPEAKER_01] Silni sukup,

747
00:28:28,460 --> 00:28:29,420
[SPEAKER_01] istoga i zapada,

748
00:28:29,420 --> 00:28:30,339
[SPEAKER_01] obtuživanje,

749
00:28:30,339 --> 00:28:31,759
[SPEAKER_01] pobijeni, dakle,

750
00:28:31,759 --> 00:28:32,559
[SPEAKER_01] mnogi Turci,

751
00:28:32,559 --> 00:28:33,339
[SPEAKER_01] ratovi, krvi,

752
00:28:33,339 --> 00:28:34,660
[SPEAKER_01] čuda neviđena.

753
00:28:34,660 --> 00:28:36,680
[SPEAKER_01] Sve to urban drugi pokreć.

754
00:28:36,680 --> 00:28:38,720
[SPEAKER_01] U svome neznanju,

755
00:28:38,720 --> 00:28:40,380
[SPEAKER_01] a ipak blaženih crkve.

756
00:28:40,380 --> 00:28:43,500
[SPEAKER_01] Valja gledati crkvu jako široko,

757
00:28:43,500 --> 00:28:45,539
[SPEAKER_01] on je imao sigurno dobru namjeru,

758
00:28:45,539 --> 00:28:46,880
[SPEAKER_01] iako se nedje izgubio

759
00:28:46,880 --> 00:28:47,779
