761
00:28:49,960 --> 00:28:51,259
[SPEAKER_01] U svetog Franjom,

762
00:28:51,259 --> 00:28:51,819
[SPEAKER_01] naravno,

763
00:28:51,819 --> 00:28:52,819
[SPEAKER_01] i drugog sveca,

764
00:28:52,819 --> 00:28:53,700
[SPEAKER_01] svetog Dominika,

765
00:28:53,700 --> 00:28:55,400
[SPEAKER_01] red propovjednika,

766
00:28:55,400 --> 00:28:57,539
[SPEAKER_01] oni su negako u isto vrijeme,

767
00:28:57,539 --> 00:28:57,839
[SPEAKER_01] dakle,

768
00:28:57,839 --> 00:28:58,680
[SPEAKER_01] približ do žive,

769
00:28:58,680 --> 00:28:59,220
[SPEAKER_01] sveti Dominic,

770
00:28:59,220 --> 00:28:59,940
[SPEAKER_01] sveti Franjo,

771
00:28:59,940 --> 00:29:01,579
[SPEAKER_01] red koji propovjeda,

772
00:29:01,759 --> 00:29:03,339
[SPEAKER_01] protiv hereza,

773
00:29:03,339 --> 00:29:04,559
[SPEAKER_01] krivih naučavanja.

774
00:29:04,559 --> 00:29:07,099
[SPEAKER_01] Jer jedno je problem u crkvi bogatstvo,

775
00:29:07,099 --> 00:29:09,779
[SPEAKER_01] a drugo su problem krive nauke,

776
00:29:09,779 --> 00:29:12,359
[SPEAKER_01] koje mnogi ljude odvedu krivnim putem.

777
00:29:12,359 --> 00:29:15,420
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, to su možda dva nekako velika zla

778
00:29:15,420 --> 00:29:18,220
[SPEAKER_01] koja mogu zadesiti crkvu.

779
00:29:18,220 --> 00:29:22,319
[SPEAKER_01] Narazimo se u vremenu

780
00:29:22,319 --> 00:29:24,059
[SPEAKER_01] avinjonskog sužanjstva,

781
00:29:24,059 --> 00:29:26,680
[SPEAKER_01] politička situacija u Evropi je takva,

782
00:29:26,680 --> 00:29:28,680
[SPEAKER_01] po raznih političkih utjecaj,

783
00:29:29,880 --> 00:29:32,640
[SPEAKER_01] crkva mora biti neki u način suradnji sa državama,

784
00:29:32,640 --> 00:29:34,420
[SPEAKER_01] na istaku nešto više,

785
00:29:34,420 --> 00:29:36,079
[SPEAKER_01] nego na zapadu,

786
00:29:36,079 --> 00:29:37,500
[SPEAKER_01] da bi uopće moglo opsati.

787
00:29:37,500 --> 00:29:40,400
[SPEAKER_01] Tako pape imaju kombinaciju sa francuzima,

788
00:29:40,400 --> 00:29:42,019
[SPEAKER_01] italijanima, španjolcima,

789
00:29:42,019 --> 00:29:43,839
[SPEAKER_01] njemcima,

790
00:29:43,839 --> 00:29:45,240
[SPEAKER_01] s kime će se družiti.

791
00:29:45,799 --> 00:29:47,019
[SPEAKER_01] Ko će štiti crkvu?

792
00:29:47,019 --> 00:29:50,519
[SPEAKER_01] Crkvu štiti Isus Krist.

793
00:29:50,519 --> 00:29:56,980
[SPEAKER_01] I svaki brak između crkve i države je katastrofalno završio.

794
00:29:56,980 --> 00:30:00,880
[SPEAKER_01] Nema ni jednog primjera gdje je crkva u braku sa državom

795
00:30:00,880 --> 00:30:03,059
[SPEAKER_01] i da je bila uspješna.

796
00:30:03,059 --> 00:30:05,339
[SPEAKER_01] Bude neko vrijeme, malo se to događa,

797
00:30:06,019 --> 00:30:08,420
[SPEAKER_01] a onda udri po leđima crkve.

798
00:30:08,420 --> 00:30:10,740
[SPEAKER_01] Crkvu štiti Isus Krist.

799
00:30:10,740 --> 00:30:12,619
[SPEAKER_01] Nikakvi vladari ovoga svi.

800
00:30:12,619 --> 00:30:14,460
[SPEAKER_01] Videli smo papu Lava Velikoga,

801
00:30:14,460 --> 00:30:17,079
[SPEAKER_01] koji sa silom Božjom

802
00:30:17,079 --> 00:30:19,599
[SPEAKER_01] ide moćno na kralju Atiliju

803
00:30:19,599 --> 00:30:20,240
[SPEAKER_01] i pobjeđuje.

804
00:30:20,240 --> 00:30:22,319
[SPEAKER_01] Sve ti Franjo pobjeđuje.

805
00:30:22,319 --> 00:30:23,559
[SPEAKER_01] Ne papa, Urban drugi.

806
00:30:23,559 --> 00:30:27,019
[SPEAKER_01] Oni koji žive u Božjem duhu, oni pobjeđuju.

807
00:30:27,019 --> 00:30:28,539
[SPEAKER_01] U duhu ljubavi.

808
00:30:28,539 --> 00:30:30,839
[SPEAKER_01] To je sila jedna na koju Bog poznaje

809
00:30:30,839 --> 00:30:32,460
[SPEAKER_01] i na koju se Bog osvrče.

810
00:30:32,460 --> 00:30:34,200
[SPEAKER_01] To je nama jako puta teško.

811
00:30:34,400 --> 00:30:36,200
[SPEAKER_01] Da vidite kao što vidite i papama je teško.

812
00:30:36,200 --> 00:30:38,720
[SPEAKER_01] Jer kombiniraju kako ćemo, šta ćemo.

813
00:30:38,720 --> 00:30:40,559
[SPEAKER_01] Pazite, to je situacija kajfe.

814
00:30:40,559 --> 00:30:43,519
[SPEAKER_01] Zašto isu zasuđene na smrt?

815
00:30:43,519 --> 00:30:46,420
[SPEAKER_01] Dođi će Rimljani pa će nam sve otreti.

816
00:30:46,420 --> 00:30:48,720
[SPEAKER_01] Ono čega se kajfa bojo, toga je zadesilo.

817
00:30:48,720 --> 00:30:54,380
[SPEAKER_01] Osto je bez hrama, bez svetinja, bez svega osto.

818
00:30:54,380 --> 00:30:58,420
[SPEAKER_01] Jer imamo kalkulaciju sa rimskim okupatorima,

819
00:30:58,420 --> 00:30:59,440
[SPEAKER_01] a ne s Bogom.

820
00:30:59,440 --> 00:31:01,819
[SPEAKER_01] I sve mu bilo razoreno.

821
00:31:01,819 --> 00:31:04,200
[SPEAKER_01] Potpuna je ista priča kada pape,

822
00:31:04,400 --> 00:31:07,180
[SPEAKER_01] se udružuju sa raznim političarima,

823
00:31:07,180 --> 00:31:09,140
[SPEAKER_01] u želji da spase crkvu.

824
00:31:09,140 --> 00:31:11,920
[SPEAKER_01] Dobra je nakana, ali ne može to proći.

825
00:31:11,920 --> 00:31:14,759
[SPEAKER_01] Redovito ti brakovi propadaju.

826
00:31:14,759 --> 00:31:16,059
[SPEAKER_01] Bez ozira s koje strane,

827
00:31:16,059 --> 00:31:17,279
[SPEAKER_01] najkatoličkije zemlje,

828
00:31:17,279 --> 00:31:19,299
[SPEAKER_01] Španjonska, Italija, Francuska,

829
00:31:19,299 --> 00:31:20,660
[SPEAKER_01] sve to je išlo iz Brdo,

830
00:31:20,660 --> 00:31:23,900
[SPEAKER_01] kada god su pape na taj način pokušavale živjeti.

831
00:31:24,240 --> 00:31:26,299
[SPEAKER_01] Zato razi jedna svetica, Katarina Sijenska,

832
00:31:26,299 --> 00:31:28,640
[SPEAKER_01] koja u sinoj muci, ona ima stigme,

833
00:31:28,640 --> 00:31:30,859
[SPEAKER_01] pazite, Dominikanka, nepismena žena,

834
00:31:30,859 --> 00:31:32,440
[SPEAKER_01] naušteljica crkve,

835
00:31:32,440 --> 00:31:34,640
[SPEAKER_01] dolazi u Avignon i kaže,

836
00:31:34,640 --> 00:31:36,140
[SPEAKER_01] papu, ideš ulazad u Rim.

837
00:31:36,140 --> 00:31:37,539
[SPEAKER_01] Tamo je tvoje mjesto.

838
00:31:37,539 --> 00:31:41,079
[SPEAKER_01] Ona se krvo bori da papa dođe nazad u Rim.

839
00:31:41,779 --> 00:31:44,599
[SPEAKER_01] Žena, nepismena jedna, ali duha Božjega,

840
00:31:44,599 --> 00:31:47,339
[SPEAKER_01] tjera papu nazad u Rim.

841
00:31:47,339 --> 00:31:48,559
[SPEAKER_01] To ti je snaga Božja.

842
00:31:48,559 --> 00:31:52,200
[SPEAKER_01] Populno isto, dakle, da li se radi o Leonu Velikome,

843
00:31:52,200 --> 00:31:54,940
[SPEAKER_01] koji sprečava Atilu, Franji,

844
00:31:54,940 --> 00:31:56,140
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, bilo kome,

845
00:31:56,140 --> 00:31:57,759
[SPEAKER_01] one koje je duhu Božjem,

846
00:31:57,759 --> 00:31:59,859
[SPEAKER_01] taj ima, rekli bi, konce u rukama.

847
00:31:59,859 --> 00:32:01,779
[SPEAKER_01] Tko nije duhu Božjem,

848
00:32:01,779 --> 00:32:04,140
[SPEAKER_01] vrlo je upitno u kakvom duhu radi.

849
00:32:04,140 --> 00:32:07,700
[SPEAKER_01] Tako, Katarina Sijenska tjera papu nazad u Rim.

850
00:32:07,700 --> 00:32:10,799
[SPEAKER_01] Ovo su pape, prave pape.

851
00:32:10,920 --> 00:32:12,400
[SPEAKER_01] imamo i protu pape.

852
00:32:12,400 --> 00:32:13,539
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, ovo je vrijeme,

853
00:32:13,539 --> 00:32:16,160
[SPEAKER_01] kada se kršćani teško mogu snaći.

854
00:32:16,160 --> 00:32:17,720
[SPEAKER_01] Zbog političke situacije,

855
00:32:17,720 --> 00:32:21,180
[SPEAKER_01] imate, u ovoj knjizi to vrlo zgodno opisano,

856
00:32:21,180 --> 00:32:23,839
[SPEAKER_01] koji su vam pape prave, koji krivi.

857
00:32:23,839 --> 00:32:28,380
[SPEAKER_01] To su komedije do bor, do suza,

858
00:32:28,380 --> 00:32:29,759
[SPEAKER_01] bi se čovjek rekao što se tu događa.

859
00:32:29,759 --> 00:32:30,740
[SPEAKER_01] Koji cirkusi?

860
00:32:30,740 --> 00:32:33,180
[SPEAKER_01] Ovaj oče vlast, ovaj oče vlast,

861
00:32:33,180 --> 00:32:35,339
[SPEAKER_01] ovako nakon trzanje, vratovi.

862
00:32:35,339 --> 00:32:36,740
[SPEAKER_01] Ko će biti papa?

863
00:32:36,740 --> 00:32:40,059
[SPEAKER_01] Zamislite kako je bilo kršćanima toga vremena se snaći

864
00:32:40,059 --> 00:32:42,079
[SPEAKER_01] u toj situaciji?

865
00:32:42,079 --> 00:32:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kako biti kršćanin,

866
00:32:44,000 --> 00:32:45,799
[SPEAKER_01] kada imaš tri pape u isto vrijeme?

867
00:32:45,799 --> 00:32:48,839
[SPEAKER_01] Ali bude onda kršćanin.

868
00:32:48,839 --> 00:32:50,259
[SPEAKER_01] Koji ćeš papu slušati?

869
00:32:50,259 --> 00:32:52,579
[SPEAKER_01] To je isto bilo povije crkve,

870
00:32:52,579 --> 00:32:55,420
[SPEAKER_01] koja je bila vezara za tu situaciju,

871
00:32:55,420 --> 00:32:56,920
[SPEAKER_01] pa imamo neke prave pape,

872
00:32:56,920 --> 00:32:58,740
[SPEAKER_01] u isto vrijeme imate protu pape,

873
00:32:58,740 --> 00:33:00,480
[SPEAKER_01] koji onda žive,

874
00:33:01,119 --> 00:33:03,359
[SPEAKER_01] kasnije su došli pape koji imaju to isto ime,

875
00:33:03,359 --> 00:33:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] samo onda pravi papa,

876
00:33:05,000 --> 00:33:05,400
[SPEAKER_01] ne znam,

877
00:33:05,400 --> 00:33:06,579
[SPEAKER_01] benedit trinesti,

878
00:33:06,579 --> 00:33:08,220
[SPEAKER_01] pojavljuje se kasnije,

879
00:33:08,220 --> 00:33:09,680
[SPEAKER_01] ali onda kao pravi papa,

880
00:33:09,680 --> 00:33:11,619
[SPEAKER_01] u to vrijeme je bio je protu papa.

881
00:33:11,619 --> 00:33:13,640
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, to je malo isto oko vrijeme,

882
00:33:13,640 --> 00:33:14,119
[SPEAKER_01] vrlo čudno,

883
00:33:14,119 --> 00:33:15,200
[SPEAKER_01] 15. stoljeće,

884
00:33:15,200 --> 00:33:17,859
[SPEAKER_01] kao posljedica dolaska pape iz Avignona.

885
00:33:19,180 --> 00:33:20,980
[SPEAKER_01] Katarina Sijenska je napravila nešto dobroga,

886
00:33:20,980 --> 00:33:22,799
[SPEAKER_01] dopedala je papu u Rim,

887
00:33:22,799 --> 00:33:26,259
[SPEAKER_01] ali je nastala pobuna između tih onda papa,

888
00:33:26,259 --> 00:33:28,619
[SPEAKER_01] koji su bili Francuzi većinom,

889
00:33:28,619 --> 00:33:30,799
[SPEAKER_01] i dakle, Italijana,

890
00:33:30,799 --> 00:33:32,660
[SPEAKER_01] koji će sad vladati crkom,

891
00:33:32,660 --> 00:33:34,839
[SPEAKER_01] kako će to sve, evo, izgledati.

892
00:33:34,839 --> 00:33:37,519
[SPEAKER_01] Vrlo jedno teško i naporno vrijeme.

893
00:33:37,519 --> 00:33:42,480
[SPEAKER_01] Sljedeća stvar nam je poznata godina,

894
00:33:42,480 --> 00:33:44,299
[SPEAKER_01] zapadni raskol,

895
00:33:45,799 --> 00:33:50,220
[SPEAKER_01] dolazi do teška ojedna situacije

896
00:33:50,220 --> 00:33:58,079
[SPEAKER_01] u kojoj nekako ljudi se muče što učiniti.

897
00:33:58,079 --> 00:33:59,819
[SPEAKER_01] Martin Luther pokušava svoje.

898
00:33:59,819 --> 00:34:05,640
[SPEAKER_01] Papa govori neka samo pas laje,

899
00:34:05,640 --> 00:34:06,819
[SPEAKER_01] papa lav deseti,

900
00:34:06,819 --> 00:34:08,679
[SPEAKER_01] tako ga vrijeđa.

901
00:34:08,679 --> 00:34:10,840
[SPEAKER_01] Ne želi se Lutherom ništa razgovarati

902
00:34:10,840 --> 00:34:14,719
[SPEAKER_01] i Luther uzima svoje peze

903
00:34:14,719 --> 00:34:16,960
[SPEAKER_01] kako bi je uništio crkvu.

904
00:34:16,960 --> 00:34:18,760
[SPEAKER_01] Novi raskol,

905
00:34:18,760 --> 00:34:21,280
[SPEAKER_01] imamo, znači, istočni zapadni raskol,

906
00:34:21,280 --> 00:34:23,780
[SPEAKER_01] pa zaradite se sve u drugom tisućljeću.

907
00:34:23,780 --> 00:34:26,219
[SPEAKER_01] Prvo tisućljeće je prekrasno,

908
00:34:26,219 --> 00:34:27,320
[SPEAKER_01] crkva buja.

909
00:34:27,320 --> 00:34:29,599
[SPEAKER_01] Kad je ušla oholost u crkvu,

910
00:34:29,599 --> 00:34:30,940
[SPEAKER_01] imamo puno problema.

911
00:34:30,940 --> 00:34:32,360
[SPEAKER_01] Križarski ratovi,

912
00:34:32,360 --> 00:34:34,139
[SPEAKER_01] raskoli,

913
00:34:34,139 --> 00:34:35,500
[SPEAKER_01] razne hereze,

914
00:34:35,500 --> 00:34:36,380
[SPEAKER_01] protupape,

915
00:34:36,380 --> 00:34:37,880
[SPEAKER_01] sve su to posredice,

916
00:34:37,880 --> 00:34:39,880
[SPEAKER_01] ohole, crkve kao takve.

917
00:34:40,059 --> 00:34:42,579
[SPEAKER_01] Evo pa možemo onda dalje vidjeti.

918
00:34:42,579 --> 00:34:45,400
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, tome su metode,

919
00:34:45,400 --> 00:34:47,400
[SPEAKER_01] smo isto poznati inkvizicije,

920
00:34:47,400 --> 00:34:49,559
[SPEAKER_01] kako ćemo ljude mučiti jedna točka

921
00:34:49,559 --> 00:34:50,480
[SPEAKER_01] koja je isto bolna,

922
00:34:50,480 --> 00:34:53,179
[SPEAKER_01] sve u znaku križa,

923
00:34:53,179 --> 00:34:54,559
[SPEAKER_01] izmišljali muke,

924
00:34:54,559 --> 00:34:57,119
[SPEAKER_01] kako da ljude prisjede nešto kažu,

925
00:34:57,119 --> 00:34:59,599
[SPEAKER_01] to je isto stvarnost naše katoličke crkve.

926
00:35:00,380 --> 00:35:01,400
[SPEAKER_01] Ne možemo joj njekati.

927
00:35:01,400 --> 00:35:02,679
[SPEAKER_01] Ona je tu,

928
00:35:02,679 --> 00:35:03,320
[SPEAKER_01] takva je.

929
00:35:03,320 --> 00:35:05,280
[SPEAKER_01] Isto zbog ljudske oholosti,

930
00:35:05,280 --> 00:35:06,840
[SPEAKER_01] mnoge muke,

931
00:35:06,840 --> 00:35:08,300
[SPEAKER_01] koje su ljudi prolazili.

932
00:35:08,300 --> 00:35:09,199
[SPEAKER_01] Među ostalima,

933
00:35:09,199 --> 00:35:10,099
[SPEAKER_01] u to vrijeme,

934
00:35:10,099 --> 00:35:12,159
[SPEAKER_01] na lomače je trebala biti

935
00:35:12,159 --> 00:35:13,820
[SPEAKER_01] i velika svetica crkve,

936
00:35:13,820 --> 00:35:14,980
[SPEAKER_01] Terezija Abelska.

937
00:35:14,980 --> 00:35:17,099
[SPEAKER_01] Nju su isto pokušali mučiti.

938
00:35:17,099 --> 00:35:20,480
[SPEAKER_01] Pod inkviziciju je došao i veliki svetac,

939
00:35:20,480 --> 00:35:21,559
[SPEAKER_01] Ivan od Križa.

940
00:35:21,559 --> 00:35:24,360
[SPEAKER_01] Njezin prijatelj,

941
00:35:24,360 --> 00:35:26,659
[SPEAKER_01] koji su zajednički obnavljali karmenski red.

942
00:35:26,659 --> 00:35:27,840
[SPEAKER_01] Dvoje karmeličana,

943
00:35:28,539 --> 00:35:31,480
[SPEAKER_01] u to vrijeme dolazi pred sud inkvizicije.

944
00:35:31,480 --> 00:35:33,360
[SPEAKER_01] Ivan od Križa,

945
00:35:33,360 --> 00:35:34,780
[SPEAKER_01] bačen je u tamnicu,

946
00:35:34,780 --> 00:35:35,559
[SPEAKER_01] samostano,

947
00:35:35,559 --> 00:35:36,960
[SPEAKER_01] pa zdravite o svecu,

948
00:35:36,960 --> 00:35:41,320
[SPEAKER_01] gdje ga nastoje spriječiti u djelovanju.

949
00:35:41,320 --> 00:35:43,280
[SPEAKER_01] Crkveni ljudi

950
00:35:43,280 --> 00:35:45,420
[SPEAKER_01] ne daju mu zavod

951
00:35:45,420 --> 00:35:47,599
[SPEAKER_01] da se previje rane crkveni ljudi,

952
00:35:47,599 --> 00:35:49,739
[SPEAKER_01] ne ljudi, neki drugi ljudi,

953
00:35:49,739 --> 00:35:51,039
[SPEAKER_01] ne ljudi crkve.

954
00:35:51,039 --> 00:35:53,739
[SPEAKER_01] On nema zavod da se previje noge.

955
00:35:53,739 --> 00:35:57,139
[SPEAKER_01] Ali je on jako zahvalan za to iskustvo,

956
00:35:58,039 --> 00:36:00,360
[SPEAKER_01] jer tamo u tim iskušenjima

957
00:36:00,360 --> 00:36:02,340
[SPEAKER_01] napisao svoje najljepše djelo

958
00:36:02,340 --> 00:36:03,900
[SPEAKER_01] uspona goru karmel.

959
00:36:03,900 --> 00:36:06,559
[SPEAKER_01] Okad je došla ona sredna noć,

960
00:36:06,559 --> 00:36:08,539
[SPEAKER_01] kad su svi poljegali,

961
00:36:08,539 --> 00:36:11,760
[SPEAKER_01] ja sam ustao i počeo razmišljati o Bogu.

962
00:36:11,760 --> 00:36:13,139
[SPEAKER_01] Tako je kako započinje

963
00:36:13,139 --> 00:36:14,719
[SPEAKER_01] svoje uspona goru karmel.

964
00:36:14,719 --> 00:36:16,420
[SPEAKER_01] Vrlo ljepe riječi.

965
00:36:16,420 --> 00:36:18,800
[SPEAKER_01] To piše u crkvenom zatvoru

966
00:36:18,800 --> 00:36:20,440
[SPEAKER_01] od crkvenih ljudi.

967
00:36:20,440 --> 00:36:22,780
[SPEAKER_01] Treba zaista vjerovati u svetu

968
00:36:22,780 --> 00:36:25,119
[SPEAKER_01] katoličku apostolsku jednu crku

969
00:36:25,119 --> 00:36:26,280
[SPEAKER_01] i u takvim uvjetima

970
00:36:26,280 --> 00:36:28,880
[SPEAKER_01] u kojima Ivan od Križa ne oduste.

971
00:36:31,739 --> 00:36:33,900
[SPEAKER_01] Nakon toga nam slijedi 30-godišnji rat

972
00:36:33,900 --> 00:36:37,860
[SPEAKER_01] između 1618. i 1408.

973
00:36:37,860 --> 00:36:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] gdje su se poklali katolici i protestanti,

974
00:36:42,000 --> 00:36:44,119
[SPEAKER_01] veliki pokulj u Evropi,

975
00:36:44,119 --> 00:36:45,840
[SPEAKER_01] sramota za kršćane

976
00:36:45,840 --> 00:36:48,539
[SPEAKER_01] koji kaže da su pripadnici Isusa Hrista,

977
00:36:48,539 --> 00:36:50,780
[SPEAKER_01] ali opet Bogu podijenog sveca,

978
00:36:50,780 --> 00:36:52,539
[SPEAKER_01] ovaj puta jednog Hrvata,

979
00:36:52,539 --> 00:36:54,320
[SPEAKER_01] Marka Križevčanina,

980
00:36:54,320 --> 00:36:57,219
[SPEAKER_01] koji daje svoj život

981
00:36:57,219 --> 00:36:59,000
[SPEAKER_01] u obrani pape.

982
00:36:59,000 --> 00:37:00,539
[SPEAKER_01] On ne brani Isusa, pazite.

983
00:37:00,539 --> 00:37:03,219
[SPEAKER_01] Marko Križevčan brani papu

984
00:37:03,219 --> 00:37:04,039
[SPEAKER_01] i papinstvo.

985
00:37:04,039 --> 00:37:05,900
[SPEAKER_01] Koje je bilo napadnuto

986
00:37:05,900 --> 00:37:06,800
[SPEAKER_01] od protestanata,

987
00:37:06,800 --> 00:37:08,199
[SPEAKER_01] šta će nam papa?

988
00:37:08,199 --> 00:37:09,559
[SPEAKER_01] Zbog nemoralnog života.

989
00:37:09,559 --> 00:37:10,920
[SPEAKER_01] To je teza Luterova.

990
00:37:10,920 --> 00:37:12,440
[SPEAKER_01] Ne treba vam papa,

991
00:37:12,440 --> 00:37:13,519
[SPEAKER_01] jer papa nemoralan.

992
00:37:13,519 --> 00:37:16,280
[SPEAKER_01] Pa u ime toga ukida se papinstvo.

993
00:37:17,340 --> 00:37:19,199
[SPEAKER_01] Savanarola, koji također ustaje

994
00:37:19,199 --> 00:37:20,420
[SPEAKER_01] u povijesti crkve,

995
00:37:20,420 --> 00:37:22,800
[SPEAKER_01] kaže papinstvo nam treba,

996
00:37:22,800 --> 00:37:25,260
[SPEAKER_01] ali ne takav loš papa.

997
00:37:25,260 --> 00:37:26,320
[SPEAKER_01] Papu moramo minjati.

998
00:37:26,320 --> 00:37:28,280
[SPEAKER_01] Ne ukidati papinstvo.

999
00:37:28,280 --> 00:37:30,380
[SPEAKER_01] I u obranu papinstva

1000
00:37:30,380 --> 00:37:32,079
[SPEAKER_01] ustaje Marko Križevčanin.

1001
00:37:32,079 --> 00:37:33,820
[SPEAKER_01] Sa dvojicom svojih kolega Isusovaca

1002
00:37:33,820 --> 00:37:35,559
[SPEAKER_01] daje život u noći

1003
00:37:35,559 --> 00:37:37,420
[SPEAKER_01] sa šestog na sedmog rujna

1004
00:37:37,420 --> 00:37:40,960
[SPEAKER_01] 1619. u Košicama,

1005
00:37:40,960 --> 00:37:43,380
[SPEAKER_01] mučenički ubijen od Kalvina

1006
00:37:43,380 --> 00:37:45,739
[SPEAKER_01] zbog obrane papinstva.

1007
00:37:45,739 --> 00:37:46,900
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, ne Isusa Hrista.

1008
00:37:47,880 --> 00:37:49,139
[SPEAKER_01] Koliko je papinstvo važno

1009
00:37:49,139 --> 00:37:49,780
[SPEAKER_01] za crkvu?

1010
00:37:49,780 --> 00:37:50,840
[SPEAKER_01] Rekla sam malo prije,

1011
00:37:50,840 --> 00:37:51,780
[SPEAKER_01] ako nema pape,

1012
00:37:51,780 --> 00:37:53,260
[SPEAKER_01] onda sve stane.

1013
00:37:53,260 --> 00:37:54,559
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, crkva je,

1014
00:37:54,559 --> 00:37:55,519
[SPEAKER_01] ali recimo,

1015
00:37:55,519 --> 00:37:57,480
[SPEAKER_01] polumrtva ili usnu,

1016
00:37:57,480 --> 00:37:58,340
[SPEAKER_01] kako ćemo je nazvati,

1017
00:37:58,340 --> 00:37:59,639
[SPEAKER_01] kad nema pape.

1018
00:37:59,639 --> 00:38:01,820
[SPEAKER_01] Ona samo tehnički funkcionira.

1019
00:38:01,820 --> 00:38:03,820
[SPEAKER_01] Sa izbrovom novog pape,

1020
00:38:03,820 --> 00:38:05,239
[SPEAKER_01] crkva ponovno zaživi

1021
00:38:05,239 --> 00:38:07,199
[SPEAKER_01] i počinje onda cijeli njezin

1022
00:38:07,199 --> 00:38:08,340
[SPEAKER_01] dobiti život

1023
00:38:08,340 --> 00:38:10,300
[SPEAKER_01] dok opet taj papa ne umre,

1024
00:38:10,300 --> 00:38:11,139
[SPEAKER_01] pa se prekida

1025
00:38:11,139 --> 00:38:13,099
[SPEAKER_01] do izborog nekog sljedećeg pape.

1026
00:38:14,039 --> 00:38:15,639
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, će budemo pomoćni našeg sveca,

1027
00:38:15,639 --> 00:38:16,559
[SPEAKER_01] Marka Križevićajna,

1028
00:38:16,559 --> 00:38:18,619
[SPEAKER_01] jednoga od trojice svetaca koje imamo,

1029
00:38:18,619 --> 00:38:21,880
[SPEAKER_01] koji je upravo da je način branio papinstvo,

1030
00:38:21,880 --> 00:38:24,679
[SPEAKER_01] a ne izravno Isusa Hrista kao takvo.

1031
00:38:27,480 --> 00:38:29,619
[SPEAKER_01] Reakcija na sebe rastoče u crkvi

1032
00:38:29,619 --> 00:38:31,619
[SPEAKER_01] je osnutak masonerije,

1033
00:38:31,619 --> 00:38:37,460
[SPEAKER_01] da je 16.6.1717. u Londonu

1034
00:38:37,460 --> 00:38:40,239
[SPEAKER_01] osniva se velika loža

1035
00:38:40,239 --> 00:38:41,940
[SPEAKER_01] s kojom započinje

1036
00:38:41,940 --> 00:38:44,679
[SPEAKER_01] mnoštvo nevolja u svijetu.

1037
00:38:44,679 --> 00:38:47,519
[SPEAKER_01] To su bili slobodni zidari,

1038
00:38:47,519 --> 00:38:49,940
[SPEAKER_01] ljudi koji su gradili crkve,

1039
00:38:49,940 --> 00:38:52,440
[SPEAKER_01] i gradilići crkve

1040
00:38:52,440 --> 00:38:55,320
[SPEAKER_01] slušaju kako svećenici

1041
00:38:55,320 --> 00:38:56,699
[SPEAKER_01] i crkva loše živi.

1042
00:38:56,699 --> 00:39:00,079
[SPEAKER_01] I kažu, aha, ako oni tako loše žive,

1043
00:39:00,079 --> 00:39:01,719
[SPEAKER_01] znači oni sami ne vjeruju u Boga.

1044
00:39:01,719 --> 00:39:04,139
[SPEAKER_01] Pa šta ćemo onda s njima?

1045
00:39:04,139 --> 00:39:06,480
[SPEAKER_01] Ajmo tu crkvu uništiti i srušiti.

1046
00:39:06,480 --> 00:39:09,260
[SPEAKER_01] Tu je početak

1047
00:39:09,260 --> 00:39:10,679
[SPEAKER_01] veliko događanja

1048
00:39:10,679 --> 00:39:13,019
[SPEAKER_01] koji ima za posljedicu sljedeći događaj,

1049
00:39:13,019 --> 00:39:15,239
[SPEAKER_01] to su razni stupnjevi masonerije,

1050
00:39:15,800 --> 00:39:16,699
[SPEAKER_01] ima i 33,

1051
00:39:16,699 --> 00:39:18,960
[SPEAKER_01] ko ponašao je Isusa u svemu.

1052
00:39:18,960 --> 00:39:21,679
[SPEAKER_01] Kažu da mastom 32. stupnja

1053
00:39:21,679 --> 00:39:23,500
[SPEAKER_01] često ne zna kome služi.

1054
00:39:23,500 --> 00:39:26,099
[SPEAKER_01] Ali mastom 33. stupnja

1055
00:39:26,099 --> 00:39:27,440
[SPEAKER_01] sigurno zna kome služi.

1056
00:39:27,440 --> 00:39:30,079
[SPEAKER_01] On je svoju dušu dao sotoni.

1057
00:39:30,079 --> 00:39:33,139
[SPEAKER_01] Svjesno, javno, itd.

1058
00:39:34,139 --> 00:39:37,360
[SPEAKER_01] imali smo nekakvih vrlo ovako mučnih scena,

1059
00:39:37,360 --> 00:39:39,320
[SPEAKER_01] pazite, ovdje ima 33 stupnja.

1060
00:39:39,320 --> 00:39:41,199
[SPEAKER_01] Na trećem stupnju,

1061
00:39:41,199 --> 00:39:43,179
[SPEAKER_01] to ima neki evo spisi koji govore,

1062
00:39:43,179 --> 00:39:46,699
[SPEAKER_01] član koji postaje treći stupanj

1063
00:39:46,699 --> 00:39:49,199
[SPEAKER_01] mora pojesti fetus.

1064
00:39:49,199 --> 00:39:51,739
[SPEAKER_01] Pazite, malu bebu

1065
00:39:51,739 --> 00:39:54,039
[SPEAKER_01] koja se izvadi iz mačine utrobe

1066
00:39:54,039 --> 00:39:56,340
[SPEAKER_01] mora mastom trećeg stupnja pojesti.

1067
00:39:56,340 --> 00:39:59,280
[SPEAKER_01] Čisto da kažem da vidite informaciju

1068
00:39:59,280 --> 00:40:01,619
[SPEAKER_01] što radi mastom 33. stupnja.

1069
00:40:02,500 --> 00:40:04,280
[SPEAKER_01] Kakve on ima kombinacije u glavi?

1070
00:40:04,280 --> 00:40:08,539
[SPEAKER_01] Jer svaki stupanj zahtjeva veću žrtvu,

1071
00:40:08,539 --> 00:40:10,139
[SPEAKER_01] veće odricanje od Boga,

1072
00:40:10,139 --> 00:40:12,219
[SPEAKER_01] pljubanje po križu, gaženje.

1073
00:40:12,219 --> 00:40:14,719
[SPEAKER_01] Imate puno knjiga koji govore o masonima.

1074
00:40:14,719 --> 00:40:17,539
[SPEAKER_01] Treba ih ozbiljno uzeti,

1075
00:40:17,539 --> 00:40:19,280
[SPEAKER_01] jer od tog vremena

1076
00:40:19,280 --> 00:40:21,059
[SPEAKER_01] sva zla koja nastoje u svijetu

1077
00:40:21,059 --> 00:40:23,719
[SPEAKER_01] su više ili manje s njima izravno vezane.

1078
00:40:23,719 --> 00:40:26,119
[SPEAKER_01] Možete to bih puno da pročijeti,

1079
00:40:26,119 --> 00:40:27,639
[SPEAKER_01] razmišljati i vidjeti

1080
00:40:27,639 --> 00:40:29,380
[SPEAKER_01] što tu sve se nosi u svijetu.

1081
00:40:29,380 --> 00:40:31,619
[SPEAKER_01] Dobro, što sam što sa raznim stupnjima.

1082
00:40:31,860 --> 00:40:33,639
[SPEAKER_01] prvi proizvod masonerije

1083
00:40:33,639 --> 00:40:34,800
[SPEAKER_01] je francuska revolucija,

1084
00:40:34,800 --> 00:40:37,199
[SPEAKER_01] gdje se ruši

1085
00:40:37,199 --> 00:40:38,900
[SPEAKER_01] cara i

1086
00:40:38,900 --> 00:40:40,980
[SPEAKER_01] papu, biskupa.

1087
00:40:40,980 --> 00:40:43,960
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, nećemo crkvu, nećemo više cara,

1088
00:40:43,960 --> 00:40:45,039
[SPEAKER_01] to nam ne treba,

1089
00:40:45,039 --> 00:40:47,159
[SPEAKER_01] mi ćemo živjeti u svojoj slobodi.

1090
00:40:47,159 --> 00:40:49,360
[SPEAKER_01] Tu su mnogi pobijeni u ime

1091
00:40:49,360 --> 00:40:50,719
[SPEAKER_01] slobode,

1092
00:40:50,719 --> 00:40:53,480
[SPEAKER_01] jednakosti, ravnopravnosti.

1093
00:40:54,539 --> 00:40:56,199
[SPEAKER_01] mnoge su glave nestale na taj način.

1094
00:40:56,199 --> 00:40:58,000
[SPEAKER_01] Što je, očito, onda malo čudno

1095
00:40:58,000 --> 00:41:00,059
[SPEAKER_01] kako se te stvari događaju.

1096
00:41:00,059 --> 00:41:02,360
[SPEAKER_01] Dobro, imamo dalje.

1097
00:41:02,360 --> 00:41:05,880
[SPEAKER_01] Onda tu je susret pape Pia VII. Napoleona.

1098
00:41:07,159 --> 00:41:09,760
[SPEAKER_01] Papa 1804. godine

1099
00:41:09,760 --> 00:41:12,460
[SPEAKER_01] odlazi u

1100
00:41:12,460 --> 00:41:14,320
[SPEAKER_01] Paris

1101
00:41:14,320 --> 00:41:16,619
[SPEAKER_01] i ima potrebu

1102
00:41:16,619 --> 00:41:18,719
[SPEAKER_01] Napoleona okruniti za cara

1103
00:41:18,719 --> 00:41:20,500
[SPEAKER_01] Evrope

1104
00:41:20,500 --> 00:41:22,940
[SPEAKER_01] i dolazi tamo.

1105
00:41:23,940 --> 00:41:25,360
[SPEAKER_01] kako ga je Napoleono sramotio.

1106
00:41:25,360 --> 00:41:27,320
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, papa dolazi,

1107
00:41:27,320 --> 00:41:29,300
[SPEAKER_01] trebao je papa staviti sa krunu

1108
00:41:29,300 --> 00:41:30,699
[SPEAKER_01] Napoleona na glavu,

1109
00:41:30,699 --> 00:41:33,079
[SPEAKER_01] a Napoleon je uzeo krunu

1110
00:41:33,079 --> 00:41:34,119
[SPEAKER_01] i rekao, ne,

1111
00:41:34,119 --> 00:41:36,960
[SPEAKER_01] ja ću si sam tu staviti krunu na glavu,

1112
00:41:36,960 --> 00:41:38,519
[SPEAKER_01] Bog mi je dao

1113
00:41:38,519 --> 00:41:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] i jao onome

1114
00:41:40,000 --> 00:41:41,579
[SPEAKER_01] ko takne tu krunu.

1115
00:41:41,579 --> 00:41:43,719
[SPEAKER_01] Nećemo mi lako biti.

1116
00:41:43,719 --> 00:41:45,659
[SPEAKER_01] Pa maka se ti zvao papa

1117
00:41:45,659 --> 00:41:46,420
[SPEAKER_01] pio sedbi.

1118
00:41:46,420 --> 00:41:49,519
[SPEAKER_01] Rekao sam, brak između države

1119
00:41:49,519 --> 00:41:51,880
[SPEAKER_01] i crkve, uvijek je opasan brak

1120
00:41:51,880 --> 00:41:52,460
[SPEAKER_01] po crkvu.

1121
00:41:53,559 --> 00:41:55,260
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da je papa bio sramočen,

1122
00:41:55,260 --> 00:41:57,320
[SPEAKER_01] išao se do dvoriti Napoleona

1123
00:41:57,320 --> 00:41:58,079
[SPEAKER_01] na neki način,

1124
00:41:58,079 --> 00:41:59,920
[SPEAKER_01] a onda se opet Bog našalio,

1125
00:41:59,920 --> 00:42:01,960
[SPEAKER_01] pa je Napoleon pao s vlasti,

1126
00:42:01,960 --> 00:42:03,360
[SPEAKER_01] radi se o papi koji je bio

1127
00:42:03,360 --> 00:42:04,500
[SPEAKER_01] jedan od najduža na vlasti,

1128
00:42:04,500 --> 00:42:05,239
[SPEAKER_01] pio sedmi,

1129
00:42:05,239 --> 00:42:08,099
[SPEAKER_01] oko 23 godine je bio kao papa

1130
00:42:08,099 --> 00:42:09,019
[SPEAKER_01] na čelu crkve,

1131
00:42:09,019 --> 00:42:11,059
[SPEAKER_01] tako da je nadživio Napoleona,

1132
00:42:11,059 --> 00:42:12,119
[SPEAKER_01] Napoleona je išao

1133
00:42:12,119 --> 00:42:13,699
[SPEAKER_01] na otok Svete Helene,

1134
00:42:13,699 --> 00:42:15,260
[SPEAKER_01] dakle je bio zatočen,

1135
00:42:15,260 --> 00:42:16,440
[SPEAKER_01] a papa ga je nadživio,

1136
00:42:16,440 --> 00:42:17,500
[SPEAKER_01] radio se nazvat u Rim,

1137
00:42:17,500 --> 00:42:19,360
[SPEAKER_01] bio je u zatvoru,

1138
00:42:19,360 --> 00:42:21,239
[SPEAKER_01] zahvaljujući Napoleonu.

1139
00:42:21,239 --> 00:42:23,179
[SPEAKER_01] Jer je mislio se da njemu do dvoriti

1140
00:42:23,179 --> 00:42:25,980
[SPEAKER_01] crkva se jedino klanja Bogu živome.

1141
00:42:25,980 --> 00:42:27,480
[SPEAKER_01] Ona kapica na glavi

1142
00:42:27,480 --> 00:42:28,460
[SPEAKER_01] koju imaju biskupi,

1143
00:42:28,460 --> 00:42:29,639
[SPEAKER_01] zove se Soli Deo,

1144
00:42:29,639 --> 00:42:32,239
[SPEAKER_01] kad to prevedemo na hrvatski znači,

1145
00:42:32,239 --> 00:42:34,840
[SPEAKER_01] samo pred Bogom se skida ta kapica.

1146
00:42:34,840 --> 00:42:36,639
[SPEAKER_01] To je simbol da je kapica,

1147
00:42:36,639 --> 00:42:37,840
[SPEAKER_01] ni pred nikim drugim.

1148
00:42:39,239 --> 00:42:41,780
[SPEAKER_01] iako pape biskupi skidaju tu kapicu

1149
00:42:41,780 --> 00:42:42,860
[SPEAKER_01] pred svetovim vladarima,

1150
00:42:42,860 --> 00:42:44,579
[SPEAKER_01] onda je se to objeo glavu

1151
00:42:44,579 --> 00:42:45,639
[SPEAKER_01] na štetu crkve.

1152
00:42:45,639 --> 00:42:48,340
[SPEAKER_01] Ta se kapica skida samo pred Bogom živim.

1153
00:42:48,340 --> 00:42:49,940
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, samo skira se na svetoj misiji,

1154
00:42:49,940 --> 00:42:51,639
[SPEAKER_01] kada dolazi pretvorba,

1155
00:42:51,639 --> 00:42:53,780
[SPEAKER_01] onda se ta kapica skida kod biskupa.

1156
00:42:53,780 --> 00:42:55,699
[SPEAKER_01] Jer dolazi Bog na oltar,

1157
00:42:55,699 --> 00:42:56,800
[SPEAKER_01] onda ima vlast,

1158
00:42:56,800 --> 00:42:57,960
[SPEAKER_01] nikakvi državi vladari.

1159
00:42:57,960 --> 00:42:59,860
[SPEAKER_01] Uvijek je crkva u opasnosti,

1160
00:43:00,300 --> 00:43:01,639
[SPEAKER_01] kome će se prikloniti.

1161
00:43:01,639 --> 00:43:03,800
[SPEAKER_01] Dobro, to je da će taj dio.

1162
00:43:03,800 --> 00:43:06,219
[SPEAKER_01] I sada se upliče nebo naglo.

1163
00:43:06,219 --> 00:43:08,400
[SPEAKER_01] Imamo dogmu u Marinoj,

1164
00:43:08,400 --> 00:43:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, bezrašnom začeću.

1165
00:43:10,000 --> 00:43:12,920
[SPEAKER_01] To prograšava Papa Pio IX,

1166
00:43:12,920 --> 00:43:14,679
[SPEAKER_01] koji je bio Papa

1167
00:43:14,679 --> 00:43:16,179
[SPEAKER_01] koji je najduže vladao crkvom

1168
00:43:16,179 --> 00:43:18,559
[SPEAKER_01] 32 godine kao Papa.

1169
00:43:18,559 --> 00:43:20,820
[SPEAKER_01] Prvo toga se dogodilo u to vrijeme.

1170
00:43:20,820 --> 00:43:23,400
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, prva stvar koju on prograšava

1171
00:43:23,400 --> 00:43:25,119
[SPEAKER_01] je dogma bezrašnog začeća.

1172
00:43:25,119 --> 00:43:27,920
[SPEAKER_01] I onda se Marija u poniznosti

1173
00:43:27,920 --> 00:43:29,320
[SPEAKER_01] javlja u Lurdu,

1174
00:43:29,920 --> 00:43:31,840
[SPEAKER_01] ja sam bezrašnog začeća.

1175
00:43:31,840 --> 00:43:33,679
[SPEAKER_01] Malo je Bernardici,

1176
00:43:33,679 --> 00:43:35,800
[SPEAKER_01] koji je objavljio tu svoju titulu,

1177
00:43:35,800 --> 00:43:36,920
[SPEAKER_01] koju je dobila od crkve

1178
00:43:36,920 --> 00:43:38,280
[SPEAKER_01] četiri godine prije,

1179
00:43:38,280 --> 00:43:39,400
[SPEAKER_01] znači, ukazanje 58.

1180
00:43:39,400 --> 00:43:41,300
[SPEAKER_01] a dogma je 54.

1181
00:43:41,300 --> 00:43:44,420
[SPEAKER_01] Majka Božja je jako ponizna.

1182
00:43:44,420 --> 00:43:47,960
[SPEAKER_01] Ona čeka da Papa proglasi dogmu

1183
00:43:47,960 --> 00:43:49,460
[SPEAKER_01] o njezirom bezrašnom začeću.

1184
00:43:49,460 --> 00:43:51,980
[SPEAKER_01] I nekada je to Papa proglasio,

1185
00:43:51,980 --> 00:43:53,440
[SPEAKER_01] ona u poniznosti,

1186
00:43:53,440 --> 00:43:54,699
[SPEAKER_01] kad ju Bernardica pita,

1187
00:43:54,699 --> 00:43:55,440
[SPEAKER_01] tko si ti,

1188
00:43:55,440 --> 00:43:57,940
[SPEAKER_01] da znam reći ljudima koji me pitaju,

1189
00:43:57,940 --> 00:43:59,460
[SPEAKER_01] Marija pobožno,

1190
00:43:59,539 --> 00:44:00,460
[SPEAKER_01] daži osklopili ruke,

1191
00:44:00,460 --> 00:44:03,800
[SPEAKER_01] ja sam bezrašnog začeća.

1192
00:44:03,800 --> 00:44:07,159
[SPEAKER_01] To je bila situacija u Lurdu.

1193
00:44:07,159 --> 00:44:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] Od tada se događa čudno,

1194
00:44:09,000 --> 00:44:09,599
[SPEAKER_01] da, evo,

1195
00:44:09,599 --> 00:44:11,260
[SPEAKER_01] očito to je vrijeme je sazrlo,

1196
00:44:11,260 --> 00:44:13,039
[SPEAKER_01] da Marija sve više dolazi

1197
00:44:13,039 --> 00:44:14,039
[SPEAKER_01] u našu povijest,

1198
00:44:14,039 --> 00:44:15,719
[SPEAKER_01] što nas u svakom slučaju

1199
00:44:15,719 --> 00:44:16,619
[SPEAKER_01] jako tješi.

1200
00:44:16,619 --> 00:44:18,519
[SPEAKER_01] Pa već imamo, dakle,

1201
00:44:18,519 --> 00:44:19,519
[SPEAKER_01] sljedeće od malo ukazanje

1202
00:44:19,519 --> 00:44:20,559
[SPEAKER_01] za kratko vrijeme,

1203
00:44:21,420 --> 00:44:22,119
[SPEAKER_01] a to je,

1204
00:44:22,119 --> 00:44:22,480
[SPEAKER_01] ha, pa,

1205
00:44:22,480 --> 00:44:25,139
[SPEAKER_01] moramo pija odraviti,

1206
00:44:25,139 --> 00:44:26,340
[SPEAKER_01] pija devetoga.

1207
00:44:26,340 --> 00:44:28,300
[SPEAKER_01] Pio deveti

1208
00:44:28,300 --> 00:44:31,079
[SPEAKER_01] se bori za papinsku državu

1209
00:44:31,079 --> 00:44:34,960
[SPEAKER_01] i saziva prvi vatikanski koncil

1210
00:44:34,960 --> 00:44:37,179
[SPEAKER_01] 1869. godine,

1211
00:44:37,179 --> 00:44:38,719
[SPEAKER_01] koji je naglo prekinut,

1212
00:44:38,719 --> 00:44:41,079
[SPEAKER_01] jer Gavibaldi ulazi u Rim,

1213
00:44:41,940 --> 00:44:43,300
[SPEAKER_01] ujedinjuje, dakle, Italiju,

